<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> cā <g type="kaḻañcu"/> lai kalam aṟutta kovi<hi rend="grantha">rājarāja</hi>ke<hi rend="grantha">saripanma</hi>kku yāṇṭu 12 Āvatu kuṉṟa
<lb n="2"/>kūṟṟattu<hi rend="grantha">bra <g type="kaḻañcu"/> hmade</hi>yam ciṟupaḻuvūrt tiruvā<unclear>la</unclear>mtuṟai <hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi>varkku Aṭikaḷ paḻu<note>The –<hi rend="grantha">e</hi> of the next line -<hi rend="grantha">ve</hi> is at the end of this line.</note>
<lb n="3"/>veṭṭaraiya <g type="kaḻañcu"/> <unclear>r</unclear>p perumtiṟattu <unclear>A</unclear>raiyaṉ cuṉtaracoḻaṉṉeṉ Ivūr <unclear>I</unclear>rukkum<note>The –<hi rend="grantha">e</hi> of the next line -<hi rend="grantha">ve</hi> is at the end of this line.</note>
<lb n="4"/>veḷḷāḷaṉ <g type="kaḻañcu"/> kaiṟu Ūṟaṉ <unclear>Ā</unclear>r Iṭai nāṉ vilaikoṇṭu Uṭaiya<hi rend="grantha">bhumi </hi>puṟaṇi I
<lb n="5"/>vūr cāvāṉ <g type="kaḻañcu"/> ti pūtaṉ comanār perāl <unclear>A</unclear>niya nāmakaraṇatā<unclear>l</unclear> cuṭṭapaṭṭa kayi<unclear>na</unclear>
<lb n="6"/>ruḷ Ā<unclear>ru</unclear> Ic <g type="kaḻañcu"/> ciṟupaḻuvūr<hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yār pakkal vilaikoṇṭu Iṉakku viṟṟa <hi rend="grantha">bhumi</hi>kku
<lb n="7"/><unclear>ki</unclear>ḻpāṟkel <g type="kaḻañcu"/> lai karuviṭai Eri niṉṟu tekku ṉokkip poṉṉa Oḻukkaikku me
<lb n="8"/>ṟkum teṉ <g type="kaḻañcu"/> pāṟkellai paṭṭaṉ pūtaṉ māṟaṉutampimārum nilattukku <unclear>vaṭa</unclear>
<lb n="9"/>kkum mipāṟ <g type="kaḻañcu"/> kellai nilakaṇṭaṉum tampimārum <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> nilattukku kiḻakkum va<unclear>ṭapā</unclear>
<lb n="10"/>ṟkellai na <g type="kaḻañcu"/> <unclear>rā</unclear>yaṇa Iraviyum nārāyaṇa nakkaṉum nilattu<unclear>kku teṟkkum</unclear>
</p>

